<h1 id='authentication'>Authentication</h1>
<blockquote>
<p>To authorize, use this code:</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight python tab-python"><code><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">requests</span>
<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">login</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">email</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">"email@forTRUEPrice™.com"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">password</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">"password"</span><span class="p">):</span>
             <span class="n">url</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">"https://truepriceenergy.com/login"</span>
             <span class="n">querystring</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="s">"email"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">email</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">"password"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">password</span><span class="p">}</span>
             <span class="n">response</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">requests</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"GET"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">url</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">params</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">querystring</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">verify</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="bp">False</span><span class="p">)</span>
             <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">response</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">text</span>

<span class="c1">#Example Usage
</span><span class="n">response</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">login</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"your_email@example.com"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">"your_password"</span><span class="p">)</span>

</code></pre></div>
<blockquote>
<p>Make sure to replace <code>email &amp; password</code> with your own credentials.</p>
</blockquote>

<ul>
<li>Ensure you have imported the necessary Python modules at the start of your script:
                  <code>import requests</code></li>
