<h1 id='functions'>Functions</h1><h2 id='download-data'>Download Data</h2>
<p><code>The Access Token recieved after login is used in this function to download data.</code></p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight python tab-python"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">get_data</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">access_token</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">start_date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">end_date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">operating_day</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">operating_day_end</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">curve</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">iso</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">strip</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">idcob</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">type</span><span class="p">):</span>
  <span class="n">url</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">"https://truepriceenergy.com/get_data"</span>
  <span class="n">querystring</span> <span class="o">=</span> 
      <span class="p">{</span>
        <span class="s">"start"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">start_date</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="s">"end"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">end_date</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="s">"curve_type"</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">curve</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="s">"iso"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">iso</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="s">"strip"</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">strip</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="s">"idcob"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">idcob</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="s">"type"</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">type</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="s">"operating_day"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">operating_day</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="s">"operating_day_end"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">operating_day_end</span>

      <span class="p">}</span>

  <span class="n">headers</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="s">"Authorization"</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="sa">f</span><span class="s">"Bearer </span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">access_token</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s">"</span><span class="p">}</span>
  <span class="n">response</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">requests</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"GET"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">url</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">params</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">querystring</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">headers</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">headers</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">verify</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="bp">False</span><span class="p">)</span>


  <span class="k">with</span> <span class="nb">open</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sa">f</span><span class="s">"</span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">curve</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s">_</span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">iso</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s">.csv"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">"wb"</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="nb">file</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="nb">file</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">write</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">response</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">content</span><span class="p">)</span>
  <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">response</span>


<span class="c1"># Example:
</span><span class="n">access_token</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">eval</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">login</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"your_email@example.com"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">"your_password"</span><span class="p">))[</span><span class="s">"access_token"</span><span class="p">]</span>

<span class="c1">#Response
</span><span class="n">data_response</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">get_data</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">your_access_token</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">your_start_date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">your_end_date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">your_operating_day</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">your_operating_day_end</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">your_curve</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">your_iso</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">your_strip</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">your_idcob</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">your_type</span><span class="p">)</span>

</code></pre></div><h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>GET https://truepriceenergy.com/get_data</code></p>
<h3 id='query-parameters'>Query Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong><code>access_token</code></strong></td>
<td>The token received from the login function.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><code>start_date</code></strong></td>
<td>Start date in <strong><code>YYYY-MM-DD</code></strong>  -format ( Earliest Available Start Date is from 2024-01-01 )</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><code>end_date</code></strong></td>
<td>End date in <strong><code>YYYY-MM-DD</code></strong> format.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><code>operating_day</code></strong></td>
<td>The operating day for which data is required (optional).  <strong><code>YYYY-MM-DD</code></strong> format. (Earliest Available Operating Day is from 2024-01-01)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><code>operating_day_end</code></strong></td>
<td>The operating day end for which data is required (optional) <strong><code>YYYY-MM-DD</code></strong> format.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><code>curve</code></strong></td>
<td>Type of curve (<strong>Available Datatypes:</strong> <strong><code>&quot;energy&quot;</code></strong>, <strong><code>&quot;non-energy&quot;</code></strong>, <strong><code>&quot;ptc&quot;</code></strong>, <strong><code>&quot;matrix&quot;</code></strong>, <strong><code>&quot;rec&quot;</code></strong>).</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><code>iso</code></strong></td>
<td>ISO specification ( <strong>Available ISO&#39;s</strong> : <strong><code>&quot;ercot&quot;</code></strong>, <strong><code>&quot;nyiso&quot;</code></strong>, <strong><code>&quot;miso&quot;</code></strong>, <strong><code>&quot;pjm&quot;</code></strong>, <strong><code>&quot;isone&quot;</code></strong>).</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><code>strip</code></strong></td>
<td>Format (<strong><code>standardized</code></strong>,<strong><code>unstandardized</code></strong> ).</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><code>idcob</code></strong></td>
<td>String indicating whether to include historical data.(<strong><code>latestall</code></strong>,<strong><code>intradayonly</code></strong>)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong><code>type</code></strong></td>
<td>Format for data retrieval (<strong><code>&quot;csv&quot;</code></strong>,<strong><code>&quot;xlsx&quot;</code></strong>, <strong><code>&quot;json&quot;</code></strong>).</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
